::Aerotaur::
      "Arrrrghhhh!"  He draws his wings in around him and falls.  On the way down some of the shots hit him in the stomache and back.  He flings his wings out again a little bloodied.  He puts his staff on his back and opens fire with his arm guns at both Deemos and Shokaract.  "Who are you anyway?"  He shouts at Deemos.
